item.title: How to make your self admin on a 525/508? any help
item.dc:creator: @Burnzcanzpwnz Burnzcanzpwnz
item.description:
@Burnzcanzpwnz wrote:

for 525 go into data> savedgames right click your name open with notepad do ctrl+f search rights should be like 0 change the 0 to a 2 thats admin if you want mod its a 1 owner is still 2 then just save it log in your admin. um for 508s well use the search button search for login.java in your source folder open it up and search the owners name delete it put your in under the owners you should see like p.rights = 2; or 1 or 0 then just save log in admin or owner.
